metadata.name: FRIDAY BEER #1
metadata.description: Created in late 2019 by brothers Jack, Max, and Sam Barrett, Almost Friday began as a collection of Instagram accounts that gained popularity as a relatable voice in weekend culture, sports, music, and character-driven comedy. Today their growing network comprises over 7+ million followers and delivers hundreds of millions of monthly impressions across a family of brands each individually generating north of $1M in revenue.
